{"title": "Death of the Gods", "description": "As attested in 1 John 2:18-19 there have been antichrists since early in the Christian Era. And that label has been applied since then to numerous sects, denominations and individuals by their detractors. Dmitri M\u00e9rejkowski explores the theme of Christ and Antichrist in his trilogy which focuses on three prominent historical figures: the Roman emperor Julian, the \u2018Renaissance man\u2019 Leonardo da Vinci and Tsar Peter I of Russia.\r\n\r\nBorn Flavius Claudius Julianus, the emperor Julian came to be known as \u2018Julian the Apostate\u2019, especially by Christians. This nephew of \u2018Constantine the Great\u2019 sought to reverse the transition to Christianity as the official religion of the Roman Empire; a transition that was set in motion by his uncle. He is the subject of the first book, The Death of the Gods, in M\u00e9rejkowski\u2019s trilogy. (Summary by Brian Fullen)", "duration": 43570, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "10774", "name": "Dmitry Merezhkovsky"}], "coverArt": null, "copyright_year": "1901", "genres": ["Christian Fiction"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "LibriVox Volunteers"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "Brian Fullen"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "Amy Gramour"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "TkSilver"}], "sections": [{"section": 0, "title": "M\u00c9REJKOWSKI", "readers": [17713], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/death_of_gods_2312_librivox/deathofthegods_00_merezhkovsky_64kb.mp3", "duration": 545}, {"section": 1, "title": "Part 1, 1", "readers": [17713], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/death_of_gods_2312_librivox/deathofthegods_01_merezhkovsky_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1055}, {"section": 2, "title": "Part 1, 2", "readers": [17713], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/death_of_gods_2312_librivox/deathofthegods_02_merezhkovsky_64kb.mp3", "duration": 952}, {"section": 3, "title": "Part 1, 3", "readers": [17713], "path": "ht